arStrings.szText: "Why are the shrines doing this now?"
I’m not sure, but… Father always believed Sanctuary was created with two moons. Legend says one of the moons descended to Xiansai, became the First Xian of folklore.
The ancestor of ancestors, whose spirit lives on in everything we do here…
I thought it might all be stories from my childhood, but… stories come from somewhere, don’t they? (slight chuckle)
